{"tid":458640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友條丁太短","createTime":"2017-11-05T05:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T05:50:40.000Z","uid":36310,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44d63c108522d34e74ab08a133f132107c73080d","tid":458640,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"我男朋友27嵗，樣貌身材都算中等，唯一覺得唔好嘅係條J比較細，平時得3-4cm，硬時也只得6cm左右且幼（幫佢詳細度過）。<br />\n<br />\n聽佢講之前因爲依個問題係讀書時都不敢揾女朋友，但依加到了依個年齡，不得不開始拍拖，因爲無法繼續逃避。<br />\n<br />\n我半年前認識左佢，性格方面都算幾match，都好開心，直到上個月一齊去旅行，夜晚自然訓一張床，個刻大家都有feel，於是就準備做，但當我見到佢條J，即刻呆了起碼有2秒鐘，氣氛尷尬，但我可以見到佢的失望之情。我隨即用手幫佢，佢都有硬，但始終只有6cm左右，佢試了插入，可以入去但我沒什麽感覺，然後便找藉口說累了，就休息去了。<br />\n<br />\n旅行返黎後，我對佢漸漸冷淡，雖然我心知肚明係咩原因，但我都係忍不住開口問，我也沒有逃避，直接說佢那太細，根本不像男人，我無法接受...前天我同佢講，你咩都好，但都係接受唔到，提出分手，因爲我覺得佢其實無可能在床上做一個男人，不如面對現實...個刻佢呆住，既氣憤又羞愧... <br />\n<br />\n食色性也，女人都需要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我咁做會唔會好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521b54dbfafe3166ffdd78c024d91d472ce91f09","tid":458640,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"我20cm <br />\nPm"},{"pid":"3022ecf2a7b307f3bfd9c271ad7e47e4cb676948","tid":458640,"uid":110683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"6cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n粗度如何？"},{"pid":"6a4bc0ab6c61ad47b7f484330fd919ec4287bb38","tid":458640,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2ebce79c483f109e7c848cbb42c5280c757414fe","tid":458640,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"女生會不會只是因爲嫌棄男朋友那話細而飛他？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=748223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D748223&d=AVe2VvwzaJ11tKqN4%2Bn9uMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=71b49bfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=748223</a>"},{"pid":"d79d08a4a514403c2f98f167fdd6ccf8a0f67bca","tid":458640,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"你長未得囉"},{"pid":"2471752891410f2c337763899e6521a79e29b4b2","tid":458640,"uid":86585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:50:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/458602/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/458602/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\nCopy夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}